flowRoot.flowPara: to realize about the (a)ether(9) is its absolute continuity.
A deep sea fish has probably no means
of apprehending the existence of water;
it is too uniformly immersed in it: and that is our condition in regard to the ether.
Aether9 is a publication of Greyscale Press.
